				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Character Creation dialog for Avatar Dark Urge\r\nThe Dark Urge is a mess, barely compos menti, horribly injured and pained, simultaneously in a deliriious giddy joyful state where they've been stripped down to their primal form: a prophet of the end, an avatar of pure murder. This should sound fearful of violence, and deeply relishing it at the same time."
